snippet.title: Johnny Depp and Amber Heard Get Crushed as They Arrive to Court in Australia
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp and Amber Heard arrived to the Southport Magistrates court in Queensland Australia so she could plead guilty to illegally brining her two dogs into the country last year.
